snippet.title: Longplay of The Powerpuff Girls: Relish Rampage
snippet.description:
Longplay of The Powerpuff Girls: Relish Rampage, played as the NTSC version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Dec. 15th, 2003. Please give the video a like! Timecodes are below:

0:00:00 - Start
0:01:25 - Intro
0:03:58 - Vote Mojo
0:30:55 - Odds 'n' Pods
1:04:18 - Jar Wars
1:31:45 - Inner Pickle
1:38:22 - Credits
